{"id":"summaries/2022-07-28-Dads-house-sellings","title":"Ford Scholar Intro Bio (Jul 2022)","type":"summaries","html":"<p>Filename is misleading — this is actually Yahir's <a href=\"#\" class=\"mind-link\" data-node-id=\"entities/ford-family-foundation\">ford family foundation</a> Scholar intro bio: class of 2021, CS undecided focus, <a href=\"#\" class=\"mind-link\" data-node-id=\"entities/grants-pass-or\">grants pass or</a> hometown, Super Smash Bros + <a href=\"#\" class=\"mind-link\" data-node-id=\"entities/osu\">Oregon State Investment Group</a> mentions. Written for new-cohort welcome.</p>\n<p><a href=\"#\" class=\"mind-link\" data-node-id=\"entities/ford-family-foundation\">ford family foundation</a> · <a href=\"#\" class=\"mind-link\" data-node-id=\"entities/osu\">osu</a> · <a href=\"#\" class=\"mind-link\" data-node-id=\"entities/grants-pass-or\">grants pass or</a> · <a href=\"#\" class=\"mind-link\" data-node-id=\"entities/al-forthan\">al forthan</a> · <a href=\"#\" class=\"mind-link\" data-node-id=\"entities/2021-graduation\">2021 graduation</a></p>\n","related":[{"id":"entities/2021-graduation","label":"2021 Grants Pass High School Graduation"},{"id":"entities/al-forthan","label":"Al Forthan Memorial Scholarship"},{"id":"entities/ford-family-foundation","label":"Ford Family Foundation"},{"id":"entities/grants-pass-or","label":"Grants Pass, Oregon"},{"id":"entities/osu","label":"Oregon State University (OSU)"}]}
